{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.1", "text_original": "陟彼北山，言采其杞。偕偕士子，朝夕從事。王事靡盬，憂我父母。", "text_normalized": "陟彼北山，言采其杞。偕偕士子，朝夕從事。王事靡盬，憂我父母。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.2", "text_original": "溥天之下，莫非王土。率土之濱，莫非王臣。大夫不均，我從事獨賢。", "text_normalized": "溥天之下，莫非王土。率土之濱，莫非王臣。大夫不均，我從事獨賢。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.3", "text_original": "四牡彭彭，王事傍傍。嘉我未老，鮮我方將。旅力方剛，經營四方。", "text_normalized": "四牡彭彭，王事傍傍。嘉我未老，鮮我方將。旅力方剛，經營四方。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.4", "text_original": "或燕燕居息，或盡瘁事國；或息偃在牀，或不已于行。", "text_normalized": "或燕燕居息，或盡瘁事國；或息偃在牀，或不已于行。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.5", "text_original": "或不知叫號，或慘慘劬勞；或棲遲偃仰，或王事鞅掌。", "text_normalized": "或不知叫號，或慘慘劬勞；或棲遲偃仰，或王事鞅掌。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.6", "text_original": "或湛樂飲酒，或慘慘畏咎；或出入風議，或靡事不為。", "text_normalized": "或湛樂飲酒，或慘慘畏咎；或出入風議，或靡事不為。", "notes": "北山 Chinese stanza 6."}
